Description: DDcentutils is a package created by the Ecosystem Modeling and Data Consortium (EMDC) Team at Colorado State University (CSU) to facilitate the use of the DayCent® model and the visualization of DayCent model run results.
  It provides functions to automate input file building, DayCent runsystem, investigative sensitivity functionality and carbon and water balance plotting functions. 
